72,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T13:21:22.000Z","msg":"部分用作購買小禮物回贈長輩或做善事；部分則為孩子買保險、買圖書、付學費及興趣班等，將利市錢實實在在地花在孩子身上<br />\n<br />\non9狗品芝麻官<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2c55f34a68e93a810a055661b0adf16e041a731","tid":1022972,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T13:59:07.000Z","msg":"估中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99ae1cdc8647f34fe942a2e2eef563933ae74fec","tid":1022972,"uid":208722,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T14:13:25.000Z","msg":"屌你老母千禧年代出世嘅連登弱智兒童又嚟冇聽過當蝗字<br />\n<br />\n利是，俗寫作「利市」或「利事」、諧音「勵事」。支那語稱之為紅包，越南語叫法與粵語相同。<br />\n<br />\n成班弱智仔早撚啲去死啦"},{"pid":"fdd73d79dd8fb07294fe7bdc3c2823a0ab409517","tid":1022972,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T15:28:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fcf97d65c2818f1985b1d2f9de28991f095993b","tid":1022972,"uid":193893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T15:38:26.000Z","msg":"有進步啦，去法庭告老豆，以前隨街捉出黎鬥架咋"},{"pid":"867ccc8d2038a357b96a14c5333c6d2c82c2b544","tid":1022972,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T09:20:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d00fd2dcc2e3058dcb5a5903f4427e94578d8974","tid":1022972,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T10:46:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f102274ac368437268cac1ff9bedb7ce5a1576d","tid":1022972,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T11:00:26.000Z","msg":"如果放係香港法官會點判？"},{"pid":"e1acb078ae0c37fa6a8968bd830998965dff9cc9","tid":1022972,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T11:18:35.000Z","msg":"中共有預謀地瓦解中國人倫理<i